text.tspan: A hacker has installed a spying tool on the device to steal your bank account
password. Thankfully, it has flaws you can use to protect yourself.
Pick a new password, in such a way that the hacking tool won't be able to guess it.
Easy version: C is not logged at all, so the solution is to
use C to type numbers then delete them.
For example 1234 can be coded as 15C234, which gives
Medium version: C is logged, but when it's pressed several
times in a row, only the first press is logged.
1234 can be encoded as 188CC234, which gives 188C234
Hard version: same as medium but the tool is smarter and
tries different numbers of C. the tool only can do X attempts.
Insert several CC so that it has to try too many passwords.
In the easy version, after inputing a first password, the title of
the keyboard will say "Confirm your password".
